Introduction

Jung Su-bin is a South Korean singer under Echo Global Group. He used to be a Cube Entertainment trainee and was supposed to debut as a member of Pentagon, but things did not work out. With his current group, Victon, Subin aspires to become a recognized musician.

Subin eventually debuted as the maknae of VICTON on November 9, 2016, with the mini album Voice To New World.
